Wanthengwa wakulindizga 6 NAH

The Bride has Waited

1. Wanthengwa wakulindizga Fumu mukwiza kwinu Mwana wachiuta zani mufiske khumbo linu Kwiza kwinu ntchitumbiko palije kuluska ichi Zani lubiro Fumu fiskani nyengo yinu.

2. Muli nase nyengo yose tikumuchindikani M'mazgu ghinu Fumu mtipe chivwano na nkhongono Kuti timlindizganinge nakuwona chisko chinu Zanu lubiro Fumu fiskani nyengo yinu,

3. Tibe maso nyengo yose nyali zithu zibale Mutipeso na mafuta tiyime kulindizga Tinozgekerenge ntchemo wanthengwa sono wafika Zani lubiro Fumu fiskani nyengo yinu.

4. Manwekero ghithu ghose tikabepo pa nthengwa Fumu Yesu labiskani tikumulindizgani M'chimwemwe tikulabiska kwa imwe na ku m'chemani Zani lubiro Fumu fiskani nyengo yinu.

Mitima yithu yiwonge Fumu

33 HC

Our Hearts sing with Joy

1. Mitima yithu yiwonge Fumu yatitumbika tiyiwonge Yiri na ise pavinthu vyose lusungu Iwake mwelulipo.

2. Muchindikike Chiuta withu tikuwonga uwemi winu Muthaski mtuba nkhongono zinu zikubusa kwa myira-yira.

